name: Dandy Bed Frame
description: The Dandy Bed frame inlaid in either cream parchment or light grey shagreen and bronze-patina brass is a one of a kind piece. This modern and elegant design creates a subtle and sculptural statement for any bedroom. The frame is sold without the mattress. Custom sizing available to suit any bed sizing. This piece is designed by Kifu Augousti, the daughter of Ria and Yiouri Augousti.
